                          With a lot of exercises this books helps you practice a lot and get used to how the grammar point would be used. Although, the book doesn't give very detailed explanation for the grammar points but is definitely worth using for the practice as it has a lot of questions which make you accustomed to JLPT question pattern.
                          <br><br> <b>Book Link (JLPT N3): &nbsp;<a href="https://www.amazon.com/Nihongo-So-matome-Japanese-Language-Proficiency/dp/4872177320/ref=sr_1_1?crid=3S2XHHDG9KMU4&dchild=1&keywords=nihongo+sou+matome+n3+grammar&qid=1591463596&sprefix=nihongo+sou%2Caps%2C411&sr=8-1" target="_blank"> Nihongo So Matome Bunpou N3</a> </b>
