      <br><br> <b>Book Link (JLPT N1): &nbsp;<a href="https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/4872177657/ref=ox_sc_act_title_1?smid=A130L4HQW02T5Q&psc=1" target="_blank"> Nihongo So Matome Reading N1</a> </b>

