  <br><br> <img src="../listening/listening_resources/book/so matome.png" class=" img-fluid website-img">
    <p class="website-detail">The definitive study guide for the JLPT! The "So-matome" series Start by learning things like contractions and short sentences and improve your listening comprehension skills step by step. Features a collection of listening practice exercises arranged by situation. -Strengthen your Japanese language knowledge and skill base by studying Japanese for specific fields one at a time -Includes English, Chinese and Korean translations
      <br><br> <b>Book Link (JLPT N3): &nbsp;<a href="https://www.amazon.com/So-matome-Japanese-Proficiency-Listening-Comprehension/dp/4872177932/ref=sr_1_1?dchild=1&keywords=jlpt+n3+listening&qid=1591627604&sr=8-1 " target="_blank"> Nihongo So Matome Listening N3</a> </b>
      <br><br> <b>Book Link (JLPT N2): &nbsp;<a href="https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/4872177924/ref=ox_sc_act_title_1?smid=A130L4HQW02T5Q&psc=1" target="_blank"> Nihongo So Matome Listening N2</a> </b>
      <br><br> <b>Book Link (JLPT N1): &nbsp;<a href="https://www.amazon.com/Nihongo-So-matome-Essential-Proficiency-Comprehension/dp/4872177916/ref=sr_1_1?dchild=1&keywords=jlpt+n1+listening&qid=1591627627&sr=8-1" target="_blank"> Nihongo So Matome Listening N1</a> </b>

